Subject: Seeking Mentorship for GSoC 2025



I’m Rohan Mate, an aspiring developer preparing for GSoC 2025. I admire your work on rdevguide and am eager to contribute.

Could you guide me on how to get started or provide advice on contributing effectively? Your mentorship would mean a lot to me.

Thank you for your time!

Best regards, 
Rohan Mate

Email:-rohanmate157@gmail.com
